    "www.nature.com/scientificreports/",
    "The test results reveal that all four seasonal series are stationary sequences, and the maximum delay order is 46.",
    "After normalizing the seasonal datasets via MinMaxScaler, the datasets are reconstructed via a sliding window.",
    "The delay order is set to 46, all the feature information of the past 46 sampling moments is used to form an input matrix, and the photovoltaic power generation power at the next moment is used to predict the output matrix.",
    "The training set and test set for each season were divided at a ratio of 9:1, and the results are shown in Table 2."
